	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If I understood correctly, there is two different PCB model for SMB2 NTSC.
<br />
<br />I want to know what is the exact difference between those two version, and how to identify which one I have. If I am not mistaken, one of them can be used for Dev Cart making or repro of FF3j.
<br />
<br />I have searched google and the archive of nesdev but I come with some contradictions in my results and would like if possible to get the bottom word on this.
<br />
<br />I thank you for your time.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
